author: Associated Press
title: Georgia man arrested in historical disappearance of woman | Daily Mail Online
text: Ex-student, now 33, is arrested for the murder of beauty queen-turned teacher who was killed 11 years ago Ryan Alexander Duke, 33, has been arrested for the murder of Tara Grinstead Grinstead, who would be 42 today, has been missing since October 2005 The Georgia Bureau of Investigation arrested Duke after getting a tip this week They have not revealed how Grinstead died and are still looking for her remains Duke graduated from the high school where Grinstead taught history to 9th and 10th graders Published: 20:18 GMT, 23 February 2017 | Updated: 23:57 GMT, 23 February 2017 261 shares
